{{Infobox Japanese clan}}

''''''Yamato no miyatsuko'''' was a [[Kuni no miyatsuko|kunizo]] who ruled the central region of the later [[Yamato Province|Yamato Province]]. Also spelled '''Oyamato kokuzo''' or '''Yamato kokuzo'''.

__TOC__
{{Clear}}

